title: Palestine Industrial Production MoM
description: Industrial Production in Palestine decreased 2.50 percent in September of 2022 over the previous month. Industrial Production Mom in Palestine averaged 1.13 percent from 2012 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 32.39 percent in May of 2020 and a record low of -26.54 percent in January of 2015. This page provides - Palestine Industrial Production MoM- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Palestinian Central Bureau of Statistics
